{"tid":1443376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台攝影師助手北角採訪期間遇襲","createTime":"2019-08-11T08:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:15:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49d2eb0787a824aa31c549b9cf28f5143e1c685d","tid":1443376,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"本台記者下午約3時在北角英皇道一間酒樓外採訪期間，被在場人士指罵，有人一度用拳頭打向本台一名攝影師助手的面部。<br />\n<br />\n事發時，本台採訪隊正在酒樓外，拍攝在酒樓內多名身穿寫有「福建人」紅色上衣的男子，期間有人突然包圍本台採訪隊，以粗口指罵，之後一名男子突然從後襲擊該名攝影師助手。<br />\n<br />\n酒樓外當時有多名警員在場，有警員事後詢問涉事的攝影師助手是否要報警，本台攝影師助手回應表示不追究。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473965-20190811.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473965-20190811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=2b0ae759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473965-20190811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a89f3c3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473965-20190811.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e12e1de8ae4fa84768e498c2b41ecc3b19a33a63","tid":1443376,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65349ca2e41cf9b25d5ffc6eaa35a2fadea01d53","tid":1443376,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6975cad9b1baf7c105746e296f19130bde599299","tid":1443376,"uid":33970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ae5f5f8f025d1576ec3342f4b64a997d11082718","tid":1443376,"uid":238697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"咁都唔追究 係咪戇鳩"},{"pid":"322b408bf4e7ff05cda117a69a023b0b8aeab0e4","tid":1443376,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2